#: 22ec8c5ba3c540a19a3eda27b1038a1e
msgid "Security updates are an extremely important part of keeping your Qubes installation secure. When there is an important security issue, we will issue a :doc:`Qubes Security Bulletin (QSB) </project-security/qsb>` via the `Qubes Security Pack (``qubes-secpack`:doc:`) </project-security/security-pack>`. It is very important to read each new QSB and follow any user instructions it contains. Most of the time, simply `updating your system normally <#routine-updates>`__ will be sufficient to obtain security updates. However, in some cases, special action may be required on your part, which will be explained in the QSB."
